<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Luna está trabajando... 🚧</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #ba68c8;
            --accent: #f48fb1;
            --bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #f3e5f5, #fce4ec, #e1f5fe);
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background: var(--bg);
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
            color: #4a148c;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(106, 27, 154, 0.1);
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            max-width: 90%;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .luna-constructora {
            width: 250px;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 5px solid white;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: float 4s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 2rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto 25px auto;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        /* Animaciones */
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.9); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }

        /* Unos destellos de fondo opcionales */
        .stars {
            position: absolute;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: -1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="stars"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <img src="sources/avatar_construccion.png" alt="Luna con casco" class="luna-constructora">
        
        <h1>¡Holi! Estoy trabajando...</h1>
        <p>Luna está recibiendo unos abrazos de mantenimiento y arreglando sus estrellitas para atenderte mejor. 💜</p>
        
        <div class="badge">
            🚧 Modo Mantenimiento Activo
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>